snippet.title: Johnny Depp - Over Because Of Loss In Court To Amber Heard?
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp and Amber Heard's trial in the High Court in London is finally over! The libel suit against The Sun and News Group Newspapers over an article that was published about him in 2018. How will the judge's verdict affect the career of the star of The Pirates of the Caribbean? Will it have some effect on his defamation suit against Heard that will take place in Virginia next year? #JohnnyDepp #AmberHeard #PiratesOfTheCaribbean 

👉You might be interested in this video: Johnny Depp and Amber Heard, Will Other Star's Confessions CHANGE Anything? https://youtu.be/swjzc_gLpjc
